      "content": "but it’s not just people at school. it’s everywhere. i feel like i’m walking around with this target on my back and people are just waiting for me to mess up so they can tear me apart again. there’s no \"better day\" when every single person you meet is just another person who might judge you or laugh at you. i just want it to be quiet. i want the noise to stop for good.",
